#: ../../release_notes.rst:28 b51e27bd522b4a368e5268fa043416f0
msgid ""
"New WireGuard tunnel UI for creating and managing VPNs directly from the "
"interface, with support for multiple servers and sharing via file or QR "
"code. Existing command-line WireGuard tunnels are automatically migrated to "
"the new UI."
msgstr ""
"Nuova interfaccia utente per WireGuard per la creazione e la gestione di VPN"
